Collophore (
Fig. 6E
). Anterior side with 15 chaetae, basally 7 spine-like chaetae, 1 thin mic, 2 inner mic and 2 long ciliate chaetae apically acuminate, distally with 2 mac and 1 long ciliate chaetae apically acuminate; posterior side distally with 7 chaetae per side, 4 reduced spine and 3 ciliate chaetae; lateral flap with 2 smooth and 17 ciliate chaetae.
